Install Tailwind CSS

    Framework Guides

     - Select Vite
    
     - Install only Tailwind CSS

            npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer

                        -D - Development Dependency
                            
                        Plugins - Postcss, autoprefixer

            npx tailwindcss init -p

    Add your Template Path

        tailwind.config.js

            content section

                    content: [
                        "./index.html",
                        "./src/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx}",
                    ],

    Create main.css and add tailwind directives

        main.css

            @tailwind base;
            @tailwind components;
            @tailwind utilities;

    Run the Project using

        npm run dev

Vite is something different placing images

    - "img" folder place into "public" folder, not for "assets" folder.

Directly link CSS in HTML file

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./main.css"> 

    - not using tailwind process like 

    npx tailwindcss -i  ./src/input.css -o ./src/output.css --watch
    



        



                    

